duties_responsibilities.duty: Develop and maintain relationships with potential clients and convert leads into successful accounts.
Utilize strong negotiation skills to close sales and achieve revenue targets.
Identify and pursue new business opportunities through lead generation and prospecting.
Collaborate with internal teams to develop and execute effective sales strategies.
Analyze market trends and customer needs to provide feedback for product development and improvement.
Maintain a high level of product knowledge and stay updated on industry trends to effectively communicate value propositions to clients.
